summary: adds small dungeon under bridge near whiterun with some loot and cells inside
descriptionHtml: adds dungeon like room near whiterun under bridge. you need to get key that can be found inside whiterun hall of the dead inside alchemy saddle. (same room you find amulet priest asks you to get) once you get it enter trapdoor and kill necromancer found inside. once done its all yours. containers do not respaws so they are safe to store in and have some loot when you first open them. alchemy enchanting anvil sharpening stone and armor bench are found inside as well as woodchopping block and cooking stand
author: 11tontsa11
